blockStates.name: Make a Simple Math Game
blockStates.userText:
This pages shows how you can make
a simple math game.

Problem definition: A snail is climbing up
a garden wall that is 31 inches tall. He 
moves up 7 inches every day but slips
back 2 inches every night. How many
days will it take him to reach the top?
